Author: Azure Automation Product Team
Summary: This Graphical PowerShell runbook returns all of the V2 VMs in an Azure subscription.  It takes in an optional resource group and VM name to return all VMs in a resource group, a particular VM in a resource group, or all VMs in the subscription if you don't specify parameters.
Title: Get Azure V2 Virtual Machines
UserTags: Windows Azure Virtual Machines, Azure Automation, GraphicalPS
